# 四川大学课表器api
<p>
<img src='https://img.shields.io/badge/author-%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%9D-ff69b4.svg'>
<img src='https://img.shields.io/github/license/2239559319/courseDownload.svg?style=flat'>
